rocket1.CGlen_i: Initial CG place from nose[m] 重心
rocket1.CGlen_f: Final CG place from nose[m]　重心
rocket1.mass_i: Initial mass[kg] 乾燥質量+酸化剤質量」
rocket1.Iyz_i: Initial inertia moment of rolling[kg*m^2]　ピッチ/ヨー
rocket1.Iyz_f: Final inertia moment of rolling[kg*m^2] ピッチ/ヨー
rocket1.CPlen: CP place from nose[m] 圧力中心

rocket1.Cmq: Pitch damping moment coefficient ピッチ減衰モーメント係数
